---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - AI & Machine Learning Blog"
  description="Learn more about our mission to make AI and machine learning accessible to everyone"
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1 class="page-title">About AI Blog</h1>
          <p class="page-subtitle">
            Democratizing knowledge in artificial intelligence and machine learning
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="about-icon">
            <svg width="180" height="180" viewBox="0 0 180 180" fill="none">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="aboutGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3b82f6"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#10b981"/>
                </linearGradient>
              </defs>
              <rect x="30" y="30" width="120" height="120" rx="20" fill="url(#aboutGradient)" opacity="0.1"/>
              <rect x="40" y="40" width="100" height="100" rx="15" fill="url(#aboutGradient)" opacity="0.2"/>
              <rect x="50" y="50" width="80" height="80" rx="10" fill="url(#aboutGradient)" opacity="0.3"/>
              <path d="M70 70 L110 70 L110 80 L70 80 Z M70 90 L110 90 L110 100 L70 100 Z M70 110 L90 110 L90 120 L70 120 Z" fill="url(#aboutGradient)"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content">
        <section class="mission-section">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            At AI Blog, we believe that artificial intelligence and machine learning should be accessible to everyone. 
            Our mission is to bridge the gap between cutting-edge research and practical applications, making complex 
            concepts understandable and actionable for learners at all levels.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you're a student taking your first steps into AI, a professional looking to upskill, or a 
            researcher seeking the latest insights, we provide high-quality content that empowers you to understand 
            and leverage the power of artificial intelligence.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="values-section">
          <h2>Our Values</h2>
          <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">üéØ</div>
              <h3>Clarity</h3>
              <p>We break down complex concepts into digestible, easy-to-understand explanations without sacrificing accuracy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">üöÄ</div>
              <h3>Innovation</h3>
              <p>We stay at the forefront of AI developments, bringing you the latest trends and breakthrough technologies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">ü§ù</div>
              <h3>Community</h3>
              <p>We foster a learning environment where knowledge is shared, questions are welcomed, and growth is celebrated.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">‚ö°</div>
              <h3>Practicality</h3>
              <p>We focus on real-world applications and provide actionable insights you can implement immediately.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="topics-section">
          <h2>What We Cover</h2>
          <div class="topics-grid">
            <div class="topic-item">
              <h3>Machine Learning Fundamentals</h3>
              <p>From basic algorithms to advanced techniques, we cover the full spectrum of machine learning concepts.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              <h3>Deep Learning & Neural Networks</h3>
              <p>Explore the world of deep learning, from simple perceptrons to complex architectures like transformers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              <h3>Natural Language Processing</h3>
              <p>Understand how machines process and understand human language, from basics to state-of-the-art models.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              <h3>Computer Vision</h3>
              <p>Learn how AI systems see and interpret visual information, from image recognition to object detection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              <h3>AI Ethics & Society</h3>
              <p>Discuss the responsible development and deployment of AI systems and their impact on society.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              <h3>Industry Applications</h3>
              <p>Real-world case studies showing how AI is transforming industries from healthcare to finance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-section">
          <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
          <p>
            Have questions, suggestions, or want to contribute? We'd love to hear from you! 
            Join our community and be part of the AI revolution.
          </p>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <div class="contact-item">
              <strong>Email:</strong> hello@aiblog.com
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item">
              <strong>Follow us:</strong> @aiblog on social media
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg-secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .hero-content {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-visual {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-icon {
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .topic-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .topic-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .topic-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .contact-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light) 0%, var(--color-bg-secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .contact-item strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .page-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .about-icon svg {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .topics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .contact-info {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .about-content section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>